15-01.jpg|thumb|Budapest, Hungary]]\n[[File:Panorama ul. Emilii Plater w Warszawie radek ko\u0142akowski.jpg|thumb|Warsaw, Poland]]\n[[File:Minsk._A_view_of_the_Svislach_river_and_Upper_Town.jpg|thumb|Minsk, Belarus]]\n[[File:Moonrise over kuala lumpur.jpg|thumb|Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia]]\n[[File:Kuwait City cropped.jpg|thumb|Kuwait City, Kuwait]]\n[[File:Downtown ottawa night.jpg|thumb|Ottawa, Ontario, Canada]]\n[[File:Jerusalem Dome of the rock BW 14.JPG|thumb|Jerusalem]]\n[[File:PortofKingston.jpg|thumb|Kingston, Jamaica]]\n[[File:WashMonument WhiteHouse.jpg|thumb|(Washington) District of Columbia, United States]]\n[[File:Paraguay Rory.jpg|thumb|Asuncion, Paraguay]]\n[[File:Riga_Skyline_Panorama,_Latvia_-_Diliff.jpg|thumb|Riga, Latvia]][[File:Southern Helsinki panorama 2011-06-28 1.jpg|thumb|221x221px|Helsinki, Finland]]\n[[File:Vilnius_-_Panorama_01.jpg|thumb|Vilnius, Lithuania]]\n[[File:Tallinn old and new, Dec 2006.jpg|thumb|Tallinn, Estonia]]\n[[File:Nicosia panoramic view Cyprus Tower 25 Jean Nouvel.jpg|thumb|Nicosia, Cyprus]]\n[[File:Athens4 tango7174.jpg|thumb|Athens, Greece]]\n[[File:King_Edward_Point_on_South_Georgia_1.jpg|thumb|King Edward Point, South Georgia and the South Sandwich Islands]]\n[[File:Cathedral Saint Alexander Nevsky (23997168458).jpg|thumb|Sofia, Bulgaria]]\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:right\"\n|-\n! Rank || style=\"width:110pt;\"| Country/Territory || Capital || Population || Year\n!% of<br>country's<br>population\n|-\n| 1 ||align=left| {{flag|China PR}} || '''[[Beijing]]''' || {{nts|21542000}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.stats.gov.cn/tjsj/ndsj/2018/indexeh.htm|title=China Statistical Yearbook 2018|website=www.stats.gov.cn|access-date=2019-07-24}}</ref>||2010\n|1.5%\n|-\n| 2 ||align=left| {{flag|Japan}}|| '''[[Tokyo]]''' || {{nts|13929286}}<ref name=\"tokyo1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.toukei.metro.tokyo.jp/tnenkan/2017/tn17q3e002.htm|title=Tokyo Statistical Yearbook|publisher=Tokyo Metropolitan Government}}</ref