ad\"] ''Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica''. 2006. Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica Online. 13 November 2006.\n* {{cite web|url= http://www.thelancet.com/webfiles/images/journals/lancet/s0140673606694919.pdf |title=Mortality after the 2003 invasion of Iraq: a cross-sectional cluster sample survey }}{{dead link|date=March 2011}}&nbsp;{{small|(242&nbsp;KB)}}. By Gilbert Burnham, Riyadh Lafta, Shannon Doocy, and Les Roberts. ''[[The Lancet]]'', October 11, 2006\n* [http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/iraq/baghdad.htm Baghdad] from GlobalSecurity.org\n</ref> ||\n|17.48%\n|-\n| 19 ||align=left| {{flag|Chile}} || '''[[Santiago]]''' || {{nts|6310000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ine.cl/canales/chile_estadistico/demografia_y_vitales/proyecciones/DatProv/SalProvUsuarios-T13OK.xls|title=Santiago: Poblaci\u00f3n total estimada al 30 de Junio, por sexo. 1990-2020|publisher=Instituto Nacional de Estad\u00edstica de Chile (INE)|language=Spanish|accessdate=5 January 2013}}</ref> || 2012\n|35.9%\n|-\n| 20 ||align=left| {{flag|Singapore}} || '''[[Singapore]]''' || {{nts|5638700}}<ref name=\"singpop1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.singstat.gov.sg/statistics/latest-data#14|title=Population & Land Area (Mid-Year Estimates)|publisher=[[Statistics Singapore]]|accessdate=4 December 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151129094649/http://www.singstat.gov.sg/statistics/latest-data#14|archive-date=2015-11-29|url-status=dead}}</ref> || 2015\n|100%\n|-\n| 21 ||align=left| {{flag|Turkey}} || '''[[Ankara]]''' || {{nts|5445026}} || 2014\n|6.64%\n|-\n| 22 ||align=left| {{flag|Germany}} || '''[[Berlin]]''' || {{nts|3748148}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.statistik-portal.de/Statistik-Portal/en/en_zs01_bl.asp|title=Population - Berlin|publisher=Federal Statistical Office and the statistical Offices of the L\u00e4nder|accessdate=5 January 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917065229/http://www.statistik-portal.de/Statistik-Portal/en/en_zs01_bl.asp|archive-date=17 September 20